      <Value><![CDATA[<p><strong>General principles</strong></p>
<p>2.1        Queen Margaret University may engage in academic collaboration with other institutions and bodies, both within the UK and overseas. Such collaboration will normally lead to an award of the University.</p>]]></Value>
